b'Sharon Parmet'
b'Biography'
b'\nSharon Parmet, News Bureau associate director\nSharon Parmet\xc2\xa0is director of health sciences and research communications\xc2\xa0in the UIC News Bureau. She handles media relations for the College of Medicine, School of Public Health, the University of Illinois Hospital & Health Sciences System and the College of Engineering. She is also the editor of the UIC Science blog.\nShe has previous experience in media relations at the University of Chicago Hospitals, Illinois Institute of Technology and the American Medical Association, where she promoted research in its nine specialty medical journals.\nShe earned a master\xe2\x80\x99s degree in science journalism from Boston University and undergraduate degrees in English and biology from Skidmore College.\n '
